1
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,399
Three,

2
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:58,439
two,

3
00:00:59,280 --> 00:00:59,719
one.

4
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,480
Let's cut the cake.

5
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,599
How to cut it?

6
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,319
Yue...

7
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,800
What's up, aunt?

8
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,000
Breakfast is ready.

9
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,280
Come down after washing up.

10
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,400
I'll wash up.

11
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:58,680
Qi Qi,

12
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,000
I'm not hungry.

13
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,080
I'll skip breakfast.

14
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,360
You can't skip breakfast.

15
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,280
Hurry up and come downstairs.

16
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:09,280
Qi Qi,

17
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,639
did you hear that?

18
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,719
Yes, I heard.

19
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:13,520
Hurry up.

20
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,000
You're eating like a pig.

21
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,560
Look at your brother sitting so straight

22
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:48,680
and well-behaved.

23
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:50,639
You're almost burying your head in the bowl.

24
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,280
I'm full.

25
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,080
I'm leaving.

26
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,319
I'm also full.

27
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,199
Camera.

28
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,079
Qi Qi.

29
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,519
Qi Qi.

30
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,319
What are you doing?

31
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,639
Why are you ignoring me?

32
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,040
You...

33
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,959
You really don't know anything?

34
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:19,519
What do I know?

35
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,759
It's just about last night...

36
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,480
What happened last night?

37
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,920
Don't you have anything else

38
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,480
to say?

39
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,959
What do you want me to say?

40
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,720
[Did he forget about]

41
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,240
[the kiss last night?]

42
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:52,839
Sorry.

43
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,279
That was my first kiss.

44
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:18,319
How could he forget it?

45
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,000
Lu Qi.

46
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,279
Professor Chu.

47
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,800
Why are you here?

48
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,319
I'm here for a walk.

49
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,240
Why

50
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,720
do you look so bad?

51
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,800
No, I'm fine.

52
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,600
Did you quarrel with your brother?

53
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,519
No.

54
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,959
Professor Chu, I have to go back to school.

55
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,519
Do you want me to take you there?

56
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:51,279
No,

57
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,800
I can go by myself.

58
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,319
Goodbye, Professor Chu.

59
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,439
What's wrong with her?

60
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,079
Did something happen

61
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:04,680
between her and Jiang Yue?

62
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,439
Master,

63
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,199
the Group will hold an exhibition

64
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,079
in Europe next month,

65
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,319
with Lin Chuanye,

66
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,680
the international master of Imagism.

67
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,600
Here are the materials.

68
00:07:15,319 --> 00:07:15,680
Take a look.

69
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,319
Do we need to meet to discuss this?

70
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,879
A new European group

71
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:27,839
has placed a large order.

72
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,079
Mr. Jiang worked hard to get it.

73
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:31,600
Now,

74
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:34,000
Black Snow won't stop disrupting our actions.

75
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:36,040
They will surely use the Butterfly

76
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,120
to brew a bigger plot.

77
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:38,600
So this matter

78
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,240
can't have any flaws.

79
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,560
Does it have anything to do with the last deal?

80
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:43,279
Master,

81
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,720
Mr. Nangong will handle these things.

82
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:46,480
You don't need to worry.

83
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,040
Qiao,

84
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:52,000
thank you for bringing Qi Qi to the cemetery to find me.

85
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,000
I grew up with the young master,

86
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:56,920
trained together.

87
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,879
When the young lady's mother was alive,

88
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,040
she never treated me as an outsider.

89
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:02,439
So,

90
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,360
it's just a small favor for the young master,

91
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,800
and a way to repay the young lady's mother's kindness.

92
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,560
Do you know my mother?

93
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:10,800
The people she dealt with...

94
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,480
When the young lady's mother was alive, she focused on painting

95
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,720
and never inquired about business dealings.

96
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:18,199
So, how would she know?

97
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:21,879
Yeah.

98
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:24,439
Your father flew to London.

99
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:26,160
You should go to the airport.

100
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,319
Yeah.

101
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:44,600
Lu Qi.

102
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:48,360
Professor Chu, you haven't gone back yet?

103
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,120
I felt you had something on your mind at the overpass.

104
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,440
I'm worried and want to come and see.

105
00:08:58,679 --> 00:08:59,279
What's going on?

106
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,240
My mind

107
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,039
is in a mess.

108
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,279
Do you want me to help you?

109
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,960
How?

110
00:09:08,639 --> 00:09:10,039
But it's all adult ways.

111
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,759
Maybe it's not suitable for you.

112
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,879
I'm not the same as before.

113
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,840
Don't always look at me with old eyes.

114
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,360
Are you sure?

115
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,200
It's not something

116
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,720
illegal, is it?

117
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:27,480
Get in the car.

118
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,000
I told you

119
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,799
to stay away from her.

120
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:38,799
Do you

121
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,039
need to ask me for leave before going?

122
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,639
Professor Chu.

123
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,200
It's okay.

124
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,320
I did invite Lu Qi.

125
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,120
If Mr. Xiaojiang is worried,

126
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,759
he can come with us.

127
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,200
Fine.

128
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,679
Mr. Chur, good evening.

129
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,720
This way, please.

130
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,879
Three bottles of Black Gold Black Diamond A.

131
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,840
You haven't finished the wine you stored last time.

132
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:00,679
Open them all.

133
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:02,840
OK, as usual.

134
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,960
C6 is reserved for you.

135
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,679
This way, please.

136
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,279
Young Master

137
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,559
It's been a long time.

138
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,720
Please sit here.

139
00:11:23,159 --> 00:11:24,440
Call me if you need anything.

140
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,080
If you feel unwell,

141
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,000
we can leave at any time.

142
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:34,320
If you feel unwell,

143
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,399
we can leave at any time.

144
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,399
Okay.

145
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,480
Long time no see.

146
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,720
Later,

147
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:46,480
why didn't you reply to my messages?

148
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,799
My phone ran out of battery.

149
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,480
I mean,

150
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:53,200
we don't need to text each other

151
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,360
every day.

152
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,679
Do you text her back?

153
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,679
She's not that kind of person.

154
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,080
Come on, cheers.

155
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,159
Your friends

156
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,440
are all pretty and attractive.

157
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:34,519
Why

158
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:38,200
are they so happy?

159
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,320
Darkness makes them take off their masks.

160
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,279
Alcohol makes them tear off their disguises.

161
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,600
There are no worries at all.

162
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,440
Of course, they are happy.

163
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,879
Come on, handsome.

164
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,399
I'll just sit here.

165
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,279
Will your baby be unhappy?

166
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,120
How do you feel?

167
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:22,919
It doesn't taste good.

168
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,120
It'll be fine when you get used to it.

169
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:31,000
Your woman ran away with another man.

170
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,279
It's normal to be upset.

171
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,159
She's my sister.

172
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,240
Let's play a game.

173
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,960
Truth or dare.

174
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:49,720
You have to tell the truth.

175
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,000
Okay.

176
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,639
Let's all play together.

177
00:13:57,039 --> 00:13:59,320
When was the last time you kissed?

178
00:14:03,039 --> 00:14:03,519
Never.

179
00:14:08,879 --> 00:14:09,759
It's your turn.

180
00:14:12,559 --> 00:14:14,080
So what's your purpose

181
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:14,559
to get close to Qi?

182
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,200
I like her as you do.

183
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:20,159
Professor Chu, don't make fun of me.

184
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,840
If you want to know if I'm kidding,

185
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,080
you have to turn to me first.

186
00:14:26,159 --> 00:14:26,879
Okay, it's my turn.

187
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,759
When was your last kiss?

188
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,960
Last night.

189
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,600
Is the person who kissed you

190
00:14:44,039 --> 00:14:44,799
here?

191
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,399
Yes. I... I quit.
